### POST Payfast (calls /api/pay)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"name_first": "John",
	"amount": "100.00",
	"item_name": "Letlhogonolo",
	"item_description": "Letlhogonolo school fees",
	"orderID": "order-123"
}

### Example curl (local)
# curl -X POST http://localhost:4000/api/pay -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"name_first":"John","amount":"100.00","item_name":"Test Item","item_description":"Testing payment","orderID":"order-123"}'

